{"tid":1824997,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"撐警藍店成黃絲打卡熱點","createTime":"2020-01-15T02:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T02:24:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7a2bfff21c1f6cb9762bd40b74b239fc323b00","tid":1824997,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:12:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200115/HF4TQKPP4KMCZ3L6IEL3GZIT5I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200115%2FHF4TQKPP4KMCZ3L6IEL3GZIT5I%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerjWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=8740e800\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200115%2FHF4TQKPP4KMCZ3L6IEL3GZIT5I%2F&h=7bb05621\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200115/HF4TQKPP4KMCZ3L6IEL3GZIT5I/</a><br />\n<br />\n撐警藍店成黃絲打卡熱點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200115/large/1579019907_645a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200115%2Flarge%2F1579019907_645a.jpg&h=5bee950e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n空姐牛肉飯老闆Annie因撐警引來大量負評。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】引發今次警方濫捕風波的「神戶食堂 空姐牛肉飯」被網民指是藍店，該店位於西九龍中心8樓美食廣場，同層有三間黃店，近月黃店生意火旺，空姐牛肉飯生意相對遜色，不少網友更特別到來食黃店、影「冇人幫趁藍店」及在facebook打卡，成為網上熱話。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大狀：拍照未違禁制令 警無權拘捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食客轟警無執法依據<br />\n<br />\n空姐牛肉飯老闆Annie去年8月在fb聲稱無法忍耐在機場看到旅客及記者被打，並形容示威者是恐怖分子，表明支持警察後，隨即引來大量負評，她聲稱生意下跌三成以上，其後內地官媒發文力撐，撐警的「大波Man」石房有、華記正能量版主楊官華及國藝娛樂主席冼國林先後拍片上網推介；亦有大批網民指該店是藍店呼籲抵制。<br />\n<br />\n同層的三間黃店是89、喇沙專門店及水門泰式海南雞飯專門店。昨晚飯時間所見，四間店各有捧場客，晚飯都有人光顧，牛肉店以中年人為主，後兩者較多年輕人光顧。水門昨晚更在fb貼文表示：「聽日有冇人可以幫手影一影空姐牛肉飯個menu比我？我想落單食牛歡喜呀！你幫我影張menu，買雞飯平$5。」<br />\n<br />\n上址食客大多對警方濫捕有微言，陳先生：「着便衣鬼知你係警察咩，都冇執法依據。」另一食客Ken指事件再度帶出警察有否持委任證執法的問題，反問：「有委任證先知你係警察，冇戴證又話人阻差辦公，呢樣嘢根本唔成立。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎家駒"},{"pid":"e826958fbdc420b86e18d5d070f5954292b430a5","tid":1824997,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:24:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n1.19 遮打道<br />\n1.22 荔枝角收押所</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HwugtoH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwugtoH.jpg&h=a3dfe053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Eq7z3V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Eq7z3V.jpg&h=6484967a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XmELBM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXmELBM2.jpg&h=0edbf756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">*連儂廁<br />\n*Twitter戰線<br />\n好 重 要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃店賀年食品</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rY7TRFB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrY7TRFB.png&h=7e3a6ef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4smjXK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4smjXK.jpg&h=8185216a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yVFbHa5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyVFbHa5.png&h=19cbaa2c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}